1) Prime Number

i)Finding whether the given number is prime or not:

let num = 7;
let isPrime = true;

for (let i = 2; i < num; i++) {
 if (num % i === 0) {
 isPrime = false;
 break;
 }
}

if (num > 1 && isPrime) {
 console.log("Prime");
} else {
 console.log("Not Prime");
}

